Release
LTS.407.2
of April 15, 2024
New features
New features added to shift function: accountYearBegin and accountQuarterBegin functions were added to return values of accounting year and accounting quarter, respectively.
Edoc functionality added: new functions allow generating files from Edoc.
Changes and improvements
Display of changed names of inherited attributes was improved;
Working with
Rating widget
was improved;
Working with
Computable index widget
was stabilized;
Operation of analytical sections in
Financial statements
widget was stabilized;
Table dashboard
and registry were improved: restored ability to transfer column names to new line;
Display of old values after audit normalization was improved;
Transfer of updates with permissions was stabilized;
Inserting elements in grid visual element was optimized;
Operation of e-mail listener was stabilized;
Display of registry with aggregation functions based on numeric attributes was stabilized;
Edoc was improved: changes made in editing mode are now displayed in attached file without refreshing page;
Dashboard widget was optimized;
Title by attribute
widget was improved;
File preview was optimized;
Working with attributes in primitive instances was stabilized.
